{"type":"message","id":"a0597ce8","parentId":"a74634ab","timestamp":"2026-04-15T16:09:27.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我这边**可用的 skills 很多**，大致可以分成这些类，都是当前环境里列出来、我可以按需调用的。\n\n**1. OpenClaw / 系统类**\n- `using-superpowers`\n- `coding-agent`\n- `taskflow`\n- `taskflow-inbox-triage`\n- `healthcheck`\n- `node-connect`\n- `find-skills`\n- `skill-creator`\n- `subagent-driven-development`\n- `Self-Improving + Proactive Agent`\n\n**2. Feishu / 办公协同**\n- `feishu-doc`\n- `feishu-drive`\n- `feishu-perm`\n- `feishu-wiki`\n- `feishu-bot-manager`\n- `Excel / XLSX`\n- `Word / DOCX`\n- `Powerpoint / PPTX`\n\n**3. 内容处理 / 生成**\n- `baoyu-format-markdown`\n- `baoyu-markdown-to-html`\n- `baoyu-translate`\n- `baoyu-url-to-markdown`\n- `baoyu-youtube-transcript`\n- `baoyu-cover-image`\n- `baoyu-article-illustrator`\n- `baoyu-infographic`\n- `baoyu-slide-deck`\n- `baoyu-comic`\n\n**4. 图片 / 多媒体**\n- `baoyu-image-gen`\n- `baoyu-imagine`\n- `baoyu-compress-image`\n- `baoyu-xhs-images`\n- `video-frames`\n\n**5. 发布渠道**\n- `baoyu-post-to-wechat`\n- `baoyu-post-to-weibo`\n- `baoyu-post-to-x`\n\n**6. 前端 / 设计 / 无障碍**\n- `frontend-design-ultimate`\n- `tailwind-design-system`\n- `a11y`\n\n**7. 抓取 / 外部内容**\n- `scrapling-official`\n- `weather`\n- `clawhub`\n\n**8. CTF / 安全研究**\n- `solve-challenge`\n- `ctf-web`\n- `ctf-pwn`\n- `ctf-reverse`\n- `ctf-crypto`\n- `ctf-forensics`\n- `ctf-malware`\n- `ctf-osint`\n- `ctf-misc`\n- `ctf-ai-ml`\n- `ctf-writeup`\n\n**9. 其他专用**\n- `Systematic Debugging`\n- `yaohuo`\n- `baoyu-danger-gemini-web`\n- `baoyu-danger-x-to-markdown`\n\n如果你要的是更实际一点的答案，我现在这边**比较确定能直接派上用场**的，主要是：\n\n- **Feishu 文档/知识库/云盘处理**\n- **网页抓取与转 markdown**\n- **翻译、排版、转 HTML**\n- **图片生成 / 压缩 / 信息图**\n- **前端页面设计**\n- **coding-agent 类开发协作**\n- **OpenClaw 配置、健康检查、heartbeat 相关**\n\n如果你愿意，我可以下一步直接给你一份更实用的版本，比如：\n\n1. **“当前这台环境里最值得用的 10 个 skills”**\n2. **“哪些 skills 我刚才就能现场演示”**\n3. **“哪些 skills 看起来在列表里，但大概率现在不可用/需额外依赖”**\n\n你回我一句“列可用清单”或者“帮我测一下”，我就直接整理。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0002bfa26c19d9490169dfb82a0a1c81978fcb74417c23c75c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":23493,"output":747,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24240,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776269351447,"responseId":"resp_0002bfa26c19d9490169dfb828fc4c819790984061f25a4157"}}
